  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK515">
<l>aṟintāṟṟic ceykiṟpāṟ kallāl viṉaitāṉ</l>
<l>ciṟantāṉeṉ ṟēvaṟpāṟ ṟaṉṟu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>(A king's) work can only be accomplished by a man of wisdom and patient endurance; it is not of a nature to be given to one from mere personal attachment.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
